-- Berlusconi to Appoint New Minister for Federalism Today, Corriere Reports
-- Tommaso Ebhardt
-- 2010-06-18T06:20:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-18/berlusconi-to-appoint-new-minister-for-federalism-today-corriere-reports.html

          
          
             Italy’s Prime Minister Silvio
Berlusconi will add a new minister to his government today,
Corriere della Sera reported, without saying where it got the
information.  
 Berlusconi will appoint Cabinet Undersecretary Aldo
Brancher “minister to implement federalism,” the Italian daily
said.  
          
          


  


        